## Purpose

`docs/` is the durable entrypoint for agent collaboration in this repository.

## Recommended Order

1. `memory/constitution.md`
2. `context/experience/index.md`
3. `context/hooks/README.md`
4. `context/rules/agent-workflow.md`
5. More context files as needed

## Structure

- `context/`: repository knowledge and rules
- `context/hooks/`: hook docs organized by invocation timing
- `versions/`: active version containers
- `decisions/`: architectural decisions
- `runbooks/`: operational guides
- `templates/`: reusable document templates
- `memory/`: durable principles and long-term memory
